               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Methenamine Mandelate Tablets, USP 500 mg are supplied as:<br/> NDC 42799-105-01 Bottles of 100<br/> Each tablet is blue, film coated, and bears the product code “105”.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Methenamine Mandelate Tablets, USP 1000 mg are supplied as:<br/> NDC 42799-106-01 Bottles of 100<br/> Each tablet is pink, film coated, and bears the product code “106”.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at controlled room temperature between 15°-30°C (59°-86°F)[See USP].<br/> Dispense in a tight, light-resistant container as defined in the USP.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Manufactured for:<br/> Edenbridge Pharmaceuticals, LLC<br/> Parsippany, NJ 07054<br/> 877-381-3336</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Rev. 02/18</paragraph>
               </text>
